\CE[94]\CE[95]\N<Jazz>Do you know a town called
Hakudeti, located to the southwest from here?

\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>Yes, that's right. It was a
fairly large town, wasn't it? And that area is
also popular because there are few monsters
around.

\CE[79]\N<Jazz>Ah, that's right. \.There has been
a disturbance in Hakudeti and its surrounding
area.

\CE[79]\N<Jazz>As you said, I thought that area
was a peaceful land without any invasion from the
demon tribe due to its location. However, it seems
that the number of monsters has been increasing in
the past year.

\N<Jazz>Furthermore, it seems that a new dungeon
has been discovered recently.

\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>A dungeon in a place like
that...

\CE[79]\N<Jazz>Ah, it seems that the sisters of
the Hakudeti Holy Demon Church discovered it. \.It
seems that it's not that big, but there are
magical beasts that even guards can't handle, and
they say there aren't enough people to deal with
security in the surrounding area.

\N<Jazz>And according to the priest of the Holy
Demon Church, I've heard that there are also
abnormalities within the town itself.

\CE[79]\N<Jazz>It seems to be something of a
sensory nature, but it is said that the number of
criminals and potential criminals in the town has
increased. Compared to over a year ago, there has
been an increase in unsavory individuals, and the
overall atmosphere of the town has become heavier.

\N<Jazz>It seems to be quite significant, but to
put it simply, the security has deteriorated. The
increase in monsters and the discovery of dungeons
have led to an increase in rough bounty hunters
and adventurers, which seems to be one of the main
causes.

\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>I see... However, if the
priest feels that way, it doesn't seem like it's
just a mere sensation.

\CE[79]\N<Jazz>I see. If it's as simple as
reducing the number of monsters and sealing the
dungeon, then the problem would be easy to
solve...

\N<Jazz>This is just a hunch, but
\....\....\....\...., I have a bad feeling about
this. It feels like there's a scent of scheming.
That's why this mission can only be entrusted to
someone with a certain level of skill.

\N<Jazz>So, it was decided that Rain would be the
one. The other holy knights are all away on
business dealing with the recent movements of the
demon army, so it will be a solo mission. But we
all agreed that Rain should be fine... and I also
felt the same way...

\CE[94]\CE[78]\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>────Despite

\N<Jazz>─────... Well, thinking that I won't be
able to see you for a while... um...

Rain>(Hawawawawa......♥♥ Jazz......♥♥♥ \. You

\OC[31]\N<Rain>Understood. Thank you for letting

\OC[31]\N<Rain>If there are no other suitable

\CE[79]\CE[94]\N<Jazz>────I see. I'm sorry, but

\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>Understood, I will take
